author: Maier H
text_description: CID- previous infection protection from reinfection
symptom_severity_description: Mild cases reported loss of smell or taste or exhibited ?2 COVID-19–related manifestations. Moderate cases reported rapid or difficulty breathing, shortness of breath, chest pain or tightness in the chest, had an outpatient hospital visit, or self-reported their disease severity as moderate or severe. Severe cases were admitted to the hospital or self-reported their disease severity as very severe
past_infection_evaluation: Antibody testing
